headers = Headers([(b'Hello', b'World'), (b'Svil', b'Power')])
with_addition = headers + [(b'Foo', b'foo'), (b'Ufo', b'ufo')]
for name in {b'foo', b'ufo'}:
    assert headers[name] == tuple()
    example = with_addition[name]
    assert len(example) == 1
    header = example[0]
    assert header == name
